    public interface Import
extends AnnotatedElement
    A representation of the model object 'Import'. Import is an annotated element owned by an ontology to specify that it imports another ontology. The imported ontology is specified by its IRI, and optionally a separator character and local prefix if members of the imported ontology will also be referenced by the importing ontology

    The following features are supported:

    • Namespace
    • Prefix
